---
// CTA Final - Conversión hacia SWI-TEC
// Diseño centrado, simple, potente
---

<section class="py-20 lg:py-28 px-4 relative overflow-hidden">
  
  
  <!-- Glow effect -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-cyan/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
    
    <!-- Headline -->
    <h2 class="font-serif text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl mb-8 leading-[1.1] animate-on-scroll">
      Navega sin límites
    </h2>

    <!-- Subheadline -->
    <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-gray-400 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed animate-on-scroll">
      Más de 20 años perfeccionando cada detalle.<br />
      Fabricado en Europa. Instalado en miles de veleros.
    </p>

    <!-- CTA Button -->
    <div class="mb-8 animate-on-scroll">
      <a 
        href="https://swi-tec.com/es/producto/hidrogenerador-universal/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="btn-primary text-lg px-10 py-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2"
      >
        Configurar mi Hydro Charger
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Precio -->
    <p class="text-gray-500 animate-on-scroll">
      Sistema completo desde <span class="text-cyan font-semibold">€2,093</span>
    </p>

  </div>
</section>
